# ─── Environment Variables Template ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env.local for development.
# For production, add these variables in your deployment platform dashboard.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Gmail SMTP (Nodemailer)
GMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com
GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD=xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx
BASE_URL=""
GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=""
# Google Analytics 4 — set in config/site.ts (not an env var)
# See: config/site.ts → gaMeasurementId
